body:

dragon

She stood naked in the smouldering cinders, pale skin smeared with ash. Not a single white hair on her body had been singed, and it stunned her viewers. They had said that it was impossible that she…

summary: Drogon My niece wanted a dragon this year for her birthday card. I’m sure he was thinking cute, cuddly, odd colour and nice. To...
caption:
Drogon

My niece wanted a dragon this year for her birthday card. I’m sure he was thinking cute, cuddly, odd colour and nice. To me, dragons are large armour plated flesh-eating killing machines.
So, split the difference and go for the best of both with Drogon from Game Of Thrones when he was still little :)
Drawn with polychromos pencils.
Original image: Game Of Thrones

Full details on my FB or DA pages :)
